Class ErrorResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • universum.studios.android.officium.service.BaseServiceObject

        • universum.studios.android.officium.service.ErrorResponse
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ServiceObject

    public class ErrorResponse
extends ServiceResponse
    A ServiceResponse that may be used to parse body of response send by a server that contains an ErrorResponse.Error object.

    Response body

     {
     "error": {
         "code": 486,
         "message": "Item not found on the server!"
     }
 }
    Author:
    Martin Albedinsky
